text:
How can I set word-completion less intrusive in vscode?
I just want to enter a newline and don't want to select the first propagated word...

elements.text:
How can I set word-completion less intrusive in vscode?
I just want to enter a newline and don't want to select the first propagated word...

text: There is a setting for that: "Editor: Accept Suggestion on Enter"
